import React from 'react'
import Dropdown from '../dropdown-menu/dropdown'
import DropdownItem from '../dropdown-menu/dropdown-item'
import{HeaderWrapper, Logo} from './style.css'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <HeaderWrapper>
      <Logo>Logo</Logo>
      <Dropdown>
      <DropdownItem>Item One</DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem onClick={e => console.log(e.target)}>
                Item Two
                </DropdownItem>
                <DropdownItem>Item Three</DropdownItem>
        </Dropdown>
    </HeaderWrapper>
  )
}

export default Header
